        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Run memory flush before preflight compaction",
        "body": "Fixes #84695.\n\n## Summary\n\n- Run automatic memory flush before preflight compaction in `runReplyAgent`.\n- Keep visible memory-flush errors on the same pre-run return path before the main reply.\n- Add regression coverage proving memory flush is invoked before preflight compaction.\n\n## What Problem This Solves\n\n`runReplyAgent` must run the memory-flush phase before preflight compaction so durable memory has a chance to run before aggressive transcript reduction. Before this PR, preflight compaction could run first and reduce transcript context before the automatic memory flush path had a chance to preserve it.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- Real environment tested: isolated worktree `/private/tmp/openclaw-pr84792-proof-rebase-20260630`, rebased onto `origin/main` `d68ba5edc59`, PR head `cb17b53ecd2c`, Node `v24.18.0`.\n- Committed non-mocked direct-run proof: `src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner.runreplyagent.e2e.test.ts` now includes `starts memory flush before preflight compaction with real maintenance helpers`.\n- That e2e suite does not mock `runMemoryFlushIfNeeded` or `runPreflightCompactionIfNeeded`. The test runs real `runReplyAgent`, enables the diagnostics timeline, and asserts the actual `reply.memory_flush` span starts before `reply.preflight_compaction`.\n- The suite stubs the embedded provider execution path, so no external provider turn is needed; the proof covers the direct pre-run maintenance ordering that this PR changes.\n\nCommand:\n\n```sh\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner.runreplyagent.e2e.test.ts\n```\n\nResult:\n\n```text\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  64 passed (64)\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: the committed e2e proof shows the non-mocked direct `runReplyAgent` maintenance path starts `reply.memory_flush` before `reply.preflight_compaction`.\n\n## Verification\n\n```text\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner.runreplyagent.e2e.test.ts\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  64 passed (64)\n\npnpm check:test-types\n# passed\n\nnode node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner.runreplyagent.e2e.test.ts\nAll matched files use the correct format.\n\ngit diff --check\n# clean\n```\n",
        "branch": "fix/memory-flush-before-compaction-84695",
